<item>
            <title>[LU-2934] Add LNet Router Priority Parameter</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2934</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the ticket to implement &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/FUJ-2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/FUJ-2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A new parameter is added to the definition of a route: priority.  This can take on a value of 0 or 1.  0 means the route has a normal priority, 1 means it is a high priority route and will be used before a normal priority route.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17808">LU-2934</key>
            <summary>Add LNet Router Priority Parameter</summary>
